Subject: Blackstone Tactical Opportunities - Investment in Logistics Tech

To: press@bloomberg.com
From: public-affairs@blackstone.com
Date: Wed, 18 Jun 2025 09:00:00 -0400

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE

NEW YORK - Blackstone today announced that its Tactical Opportunities fund (BXTO) has made a $250 million strategic investment in LogiChain Solutions, a platform for supply chain visibility.

- Deal: Project ChainLink (Growth Equity)
- Target: LogiChain Solutions
- Sector: Air Freight & Logistics (GICS: 20301010)

This investment reflects Blackstone's commitment to identifying high-growth, technology-enabled businesses that are transforming traditional industries.

